channel.title: Need someone to help you with your 317?
channel.description:
Im here to help. Im DjGrvzz and I want to get back into Rsps, but I cannot host anymore. So I was wondering, if anyone needs a coder, or a helping hand around there server, Im here to help :D I can help with almost everything, from port forwarding, to design with new Training places or even a new home! Ive been in RSPS for 5 years, coded for 4. Ill even stay to play the server :D Just email me at grvzdavdubz@yahoo.com.
(MOD NOTE: Don't know if any of this is against rules or in wrong section so please move if it is, Sorry for the inconvenience.)
